   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Ã MONSIEUR GUSTAVE MAÃON<text:line-break/><text:line-break/>Amical souvenir de son voisin<text:line-break/>du Pavillon dâEnghien Ã  Chantilly.<text:line-break/></text:p>
